{"tid":913532,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[食鬼食評]-堅料豬手車仔麵(0/10分)","createTime":"2018-11-23T13:01:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-25T08:00:33.000Z","uid":182683,"like":11,"dislike":49,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"304be1c387a51ad0c852a21f491991797006d6fe","tid":913532,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T13:01:39.000Z","msg":"真係堅料！我第一次比0分！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實間野啲野食正常，啲伙記都好好人，但野食入面有膠片，永遠黑名單！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wwK0NU5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwwK0NU5.png&h=7c06e94e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j6Pj3tr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj6Pj3tr.png&h=9fab7239&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R8vfBOs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR8vfBOs.png&h=799178e3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f3LZ3tt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff3LZ3tt.png&h=4f66b2e1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PPucD1O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPPucD1O.png&h=2ddbe5fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食評我就唔打啦，啲相想睇自己校番彩色！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為就算煮到曉飛，但食到膠片已經唔駛再講！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個煲仔飯仲要預訂先有！！！個阿姐幫我裝飯，我第一啖就食到膠片，自然反應吐番出黎比佢睇，跟手佢就拎走左而我冇影到相。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁岩同囡囡一齊，佢比較平和個人，唔鍾意同人吵，所以我見間野都冇咩表示剩係講左句對唔住，我都忍住冇做啲咩！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過本人已報食環！！！盡曬力！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我好少遇到咁嘅情況，我返到屋企問啲朋友遇到會點做，但大部份都係答我：平嘅咪算，貴先屌7佢，大排檔同茶記個啲唔乾淨好正常。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我一直都唔明點解平就可以算，同埋香港有啲人好似覺得有某啲餐廳唔乾淨係正常嘅事，有啲大排擋直情坐係街食有老鼠小強陪住你食就比個名叫&rdquo;風味&rdquo;。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解硬係要搵啲野美化唔乾淨同求其！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家遇到咁嘅情況通常會點做？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n評分：0/10<br />\n評語：膠片煲仔飯<br />\n溝女指數：0/10<br />\n食到囡囡好唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nIg:<a href=\"https://instagram.com/hkfoodghost/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fhkfoodghost%2F&d=lXrYz4C0qATswibqBtwHxjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=bc99999f\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/hkfoodghost/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"479e17af1605f2625e5cd747834a526d9091c190","tid":913532,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T13:13:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"009275709acb3995301e9c3467bad3b179840feb","tid":913532,"uid":44333,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T13:16:33.000Z","msg":"我唔直接去答你, 用例子答<br />\n我頭先去街, 想食野 見到有兩間差唔多係連住既茶餐廳<br />\n<br />\n一間夜晚呢個鐘數係主要賣潮州粉麵, 另一間係車仔麵 潮州粉麵果間係門口睇到 D 麵幾錢碗, 跟野飲/油菜又幾錢(當然係平過就咁叫) 車仔麵果間無得睇係咩價錢<br />\n<br />\n因為我好耐無食過車仔麵, 所以揀左車仔麵 (但係我既習慣係, 唔列明價錢既餐館我係一律唔去, 今次係例外, 係一次好悲哀既例外 )<br />\n<br />\n入到去車仔麵間野 粗幼麵果 D $9 出前一丁 $11 &quot;食送&quot; 貴既 $6, 平既 $5 我食開三 &quot;食送&quot; , 淨係碗麵已經 $28 野飲無得平, $11 凍飲<br />\n<br />\n食就要埋單 $39, 仲未計我計劃叫埋油菜<br />\n<br />\n我再望下佢個 &quot;廚房&quot; (車仔麵通常係o係出面架嘛) 一定唔算係乾淨果隻<br />\n<br />\n我問佢有無平 D 既野呀咁<br />\n<br />\n有, $10 腸份, $10 粉果(佢建議) $10 三隻粉果<br />\n<br />\n我---&gt;即走<br />\n<br />\n跟住去左果間潮州粉麵 雙拼麵 + 油菜 + 野飲 埋單 $35<br />\n<br />\n仲要食左好靚既豬手 三舊有半個拳頭咁大既豬手, (仲要我碗係雙拼麵, 有兩樣 &quot;食送&quot;), 三舊豬手食晒<br />\n<br />\n上面講左乜野, 自己參透下啦"},{"pid":"f8830e2047ea7d568e6526a8ff51c7491c92822e","tid":913532,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T13:46:21.000Z","msg":"冇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"485929c860acff399024c3a856d20887b48291ee","tid":913532,"uid":54264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T13:53:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">囡囡好唔開心</span></span>先至係重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"499891294a1c47318820f2e6c1f423e5d6faff94","tid":913532,"uid":41407,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"485929c860acff399024c3a856d20887b48291ee","tid":913532,"uid":54264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T13:53:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">囡囡好唔開心</span></span>先至係重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T14:05:17.000Z","msg":"偽毒可恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0c6ad81980c62a8b6b8368cdf0529f821b09f8b","tid":913532,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T14:24:58.000Z","msg":"星期五咁少人 個個去曬食女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"500c242ea65976184d8d5494501b39cbbf72f56d","tid":913532,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"009275709acb3995301e9c3467bad3b179840feb","tid":913532,"uid":44333,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-2